Class MessageResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • retrieval.client.message.MessageResults

  • public class MessageResults
extends java.lang.Object
    Message for XML results Many servers will send this message to a central server (similar pitcures). A Central server will send this message to a client (similar pictures + server state) and a list of server state
